1) details on this link from where its inspired:
https://magento.stackexchange.com/questions/39981/how-can-i-bootstrap-magento-2-in-a-test-php-script

2) Copy two files test  TestApp in folder folder pub
3) Add your file path in TestApp.php for execution this can be cron or any other file
4) ping this files function which you want to test
5) Then run this in browser

